name: #8 GREED
description: Legend of the fortune of fools was told far and wide. Greed the devil with tricks as they called him. Hunters were warned to keep their urges hidden as Greed would sweep into their souls and reveal their deepest darkest desires, enchanting their weakening will towards the fortune of fools. A promise of gold that lured them towards the poisonous pit of the seven-headed serpent.
